pageContext.claim: “And if they don't do something with Seattle, we're going to do that. We're going to go in there, because what's happening -- they're taking over American cities. By the way, in all cases, it's Democrats; they're Democrat run in all cases. And Joe Biden would have that be the whole country. It's so crazy what's happening.”
pageContext.analysis: The mostly peaceful protests over police brutality are taking place in cities across the country run by officials from both parties.
